metadata.name: Squirmees #1
metadata.description:
“Squirmees is a story of a colorful kind,  
born from the cosmos, the beginning of time.  
Each one special, each one unique,  
all shapes and sizes from their head to their feet.”  
—  
Squirmees is a story driven universe where each chapter unlocks new adventures and new possibilities. 500 Squirmees to collect in Series 1, the Genesis collection. 

Each Squirmees is 1/1 hand drawn, non-generative, truly one-of-a-kind pieces of art - created and drawn by Rudy The Artist  
—  
Read the story at www.squirmees.com  
Squirmees art prints: visit website or DM for crypto purchase  
Squirmees community: twitter @rudytheartist
